languages.text:
Крепко вцепившись в глотки друг друга,
Насмерть боролись бойцы.
Убыло сил у обоих, однако еще
Довольно осталось у зверя коварства".

Each the other's throat seizing,
the warriors fought to the death.
Both were flagging,
but of cunning
the beast had enough
yet in store."

languages.text:
互いの喉元を掴み
戦士たちは死闘を繰り広げた
どちらも衰弱していたが
狡猾な獣は
まだまだ余力を
残していた」

languages.text:
“双方都扼住了对方的咽喉。
这是一场殊死的搏斗，
两人都已精疲力尽。
但论狡诈，
天生的禽兽，
恐怕技高一筹。”
languages.original_text:
Each the other's throat seizing,
the warriors fought to the death.
Both were flagging,
but of cunning
the beast had enough
yet in store."

languages.text:
« Chacun d'eux à la gorge
saisit son adversaire
et les guerriers se livrèrent
un combat à mort.
Tous deux s'épuisaient,
mais de ruse la bête
ne manquait point. »
languages.original_text:

the warriors fought to the death.
Both were flagging,
but of cunning
the beast had enough
yet in store."

languages.text:
«Con la garganta del rival en sus manos,
ambos guerreros lucharon hasta la muerte.
Flaqueaban ya ambos,
pero argucias
aún tenía la bestia
preparadas a la espera».

languages.text:
Jeder dem anderen an die Kehle gehend
kämpften die Krieger bis zum Tod.
Beiden schwanden die Kräfte,
doch List und Tücke
hatte das Untier noch
genügend im Leib."

languages.text:
Birbirlerinin boğazına yapıştılar,
Ölümüne savaştı savaşçılar.
İkisi de güçsüzdü
Fakat sinsice planları boldu.
Canavarın göstermediği
Daha çok şey vardı."
